## PR Gate Policy

- Block approval if:
  - Branch name does not match `^story/[0-9]+(\.[0-9]+)*-[a-z0-9-]+$`
  - PR title/body is missing a story id reference (`story ${id}` | `story-${id}` | `story/${id}` | `story: ${id}`)
- Request Dev to rename the branch and/or update the PR before proceeding.
